laboratory_examinations.findings: Estimated GFR = 53 if non African-American, Estimated GFR = 65 if African-American. GFR<60 = Chronic Kidney Disease.

Slightly increased echogenicity of the liver suggesting fatty infiltration, no focal hepatic lesions or masses, gallbladder contains sludge and tiny echogenic stones, gallbladder wall up to 4 mm thick, small amount of pericholecystic fluid, CBD unremarkable at 6 mm.
